      • bindAndGetSparql

        String bindAndGetSparql()
        If the engine that will run this Executor doesn't support bindings, then this function can simulate bindings. It is strictly an alternate to calling setBindings(org.openrdf.query.Operation, org.openrdf.model.ValueFactory) followed by getSparql() when your engine doesn't support this behavior.
        Returns:
        the Sparql string, with all the bindings replaced
